<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span> ضعيف ـ <span class="c2">((غاية المرام)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢٩٩)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو حَاتِمٍ:</span> الطَّرْقُ: التَّنْجِيمُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
